---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-8">About Me</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg">
      <p>
        Hi there! I'm a passionate developer who loves creating beautiful and functional web applications.
        This blog is where I share my experiences, insights, and lessons learned along my journey.
      </p>
      
      <h2>My Background</h2>
      <p>
        I've been working in web development for several years, focusing on modern technologies
        and best practices. My expertise includes JavaScript, TypeScript, React, and various other
        web technologies.
      </p>

      <h2>Why I Write</h2>
      <p>
        I believe in sharing knowledge and helping others learn from my experiences. Through this
        blog, I aim to contribute to the web development community and connect with fellow developers.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>